{"tid":1954803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黃色經濟圈】集思廣益 疫情之下有咩方法救救黃店","createTime":"2020-04-02T05:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T10:56:25.000Z","uid":24066,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"87327fc313a435cb137d17c66ff58f7ca79ac01f","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:33:59.000Z","msg":"有鑒於最近武漢肺炎疫情嚴重，好多黃店（不論飲食、零售定服務業）都宣布告急，甚至已經結業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗每次外出食飯只食黃店之外，大家不如一齊諗下有咩方法可以鞏固黃色經濟圈，幫黃店渡過呢次武肺？<br />\n<br />\n以下我拋磚引玉，提出三個方法，希望大家入嚟一齊集思廣益。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e154c1e7ba94c48efddc25c8c16be05c59e5f866","tid":1954803,"uid":325840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:35:11.000Z","msg":"外賣/黃券<br />\n<br />\n原來可以咁樣幫還押手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1954173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1954173</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1764f13e4bd15f7b4398169ede509e7cf0d73c07","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:35:29.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong>1. 黃店排隊APP</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n現時黃店APP有好多，例如whatsgap、wolipay、和你eat等等，佢哋主要嘅功能係提供黃店資訊。<br />\n<br />\n根據呢啲APP，我認為可以開拓一個功能，顯示每間黃店大概客滿量/排隊時間畀用戶睇。如果某間黃店已經客滿，黃店APP仲可以顯示埋附近(e.g. 一公里內)其他黃店。<br />\n<br />\nAPP用戶可以參考返每間黃店多唔多生意，或者每間黃店要排幾耐隊先有位，從而考慮下幫襯邊間黃店。<br />\n<br />\n現時政府規管每間食肆只可以開放一半座位，令餐廳嘅人客人數少咗。某啲知名嘅黃店可能會因此出現排隊，另一邊廂較少知名度嘅黃店可能會拍晒烏蠅。呢個黃店排隊APP就係希望透過分散黃店嘅光顧率，紓緩以上情況。"},{"pid":"8d9aaef443c615d2d8a09db947c12603a99da29a","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong>2. 飲品店同附近餐廳合作</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈入面，有唔少都係飲品店。本來飲品店喺香港都幾受歡迎，尤其是學生。<br />\n<br />\n但係武肺一開始，一嚟少咗人出街，二嚟因為唔衛生少咗好多人會邊行邊飲。<br />\n<br />\n參考返將軍澳BEANS嘅做法，佢哋有同對面茶飲店「我想和你無所事事」合作，餐飲可以用優惠價轉飲茶飲店嘅飲品。<br />\n<br />\n飲品店可以同附近嘅黃店餐廳合作，喺餐廳可以用優惠價轉飲品，之後由飲品店送過去餐廳。<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法一嚟可以等人坐定定飲衛生啲，二嚟就算間飲品店位置隱蔽都可以多啲人幫襯。"},{"pid":"c7cf0427b0a0e5d3c846f5e02dc289bdda86bd0f","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:36:00.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong>3. 小店聯合提供座位</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈入面，有唔少都係適合「掃街」嘅小店，例如葵涌廣場、太安樓、旺角新之城等等。本來呢啲小店喺香港都幾受歡迎，尤其是學生。<br />\n<br />\n但係武肺一開始，一嚟少咗人出街，二嚟因為唔衛生少咗好多人會邊行邊食。<br />\n<br />\n一個商場/地區內嘅小店，可以合租一個舖位/位置，只要有幫襯其中一間小店，就可以入內飲食。<br />\n<br />\n呢個方法可以等人坐定定食衛生啲。"},{"pid":"35b215ae6a1e5e49cf906058fc204562c7ce3256","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\n希望做唔住嘅黃店推出飯券&quot;預先付款&quot;<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1953880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1953880</a>"},{"pid":"f0c5559181f9e35c40fa2b726279042ff6677125","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:38:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06203e5d43463aae22e62c3867098f4e94dd716b","tid":1954803,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"現金券，疫情之後再幫襯，如果執笠先退$"},{"pid":"f692fdabf2248df1d9e5d4d7dc9ac423303dcb48","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e7e401b849bdd35e5ebff9ca8d61d38d4bdd90","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43a86d6c2602d333530b015b7fa80dea2234908","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e154c1e7ba94c48efddc25c8c16be05c59e5f866","tid":1954803,"uid":325840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:35:11.000Z","msg":"外賣/黃券<br />\n<br />\n原來可以咁樣幫還押手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1954173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1954173</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:45:06.000Z","msg":"宜家有外賣自取APP「拎duck」<br />\n<br />\n但係外賣送上門暫時只得foodpanda, Deliveroo, ubereats呢類APP，佢哋抽佣抽好多，變相令黃店賺好少。<br />\n<br />\n有無可以替代嘅方法呢？"},{"pid":"3f9e875e55a3c5ccb1d43495e8b9f37bc251c306","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:49:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0aa0b883f4c462a2412c791e39526d82c19ef02","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:50:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847326d0a84bc05990cd71bb6a436c5d2f19540f","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14753dfc83c7c2ee905f43e63f79fb3640a7563","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca1ad15c7fb511e2bb617e766d09290f8aa8eb8","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c967e5f8066a04baacab17120fd60b2c48df34","tid":1954803,"uid":24066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:51:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83ae10f3748b72f56119546a9646724dcce9fd7","tid":1954803,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T05:51:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0be7253127add644de6042f97403373998089b4d","tid":1954803,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2